	TaintedCloudberry: Combine 1 Life Fruit, 10 Uelibloom Bar and 8 Divine Geode
	SacredStrawberry: Combine 1 Life Fruit, 5 Yharon Soul Fragment and 1 Ascendent Spirit Essence
