	CometShard: Combine 10 each Meteorite Bar and Fallen Star and 50 Starblight Soot
	EtherealCore: Combine 20 each Nebula Fragment Fallen Star and 25 Astral Bar
	PhantomHeart: Combine 5 Ruinous Soul and 25 Necroplasm
