	InfernalBlood: Drops from Ravager in Revengeance or Death Mode only
	RedLightningContainer: Drops from Dragonfolly in Revengeance or Death Mode only
	ElectrolyteGelPack: Drops from Slime God in Revengeance or Death Mode only
	StarlightFuelCell: Drops from Astrum Aureus in Revengeance or Death Mode only
	Ectoheart: Drops from Polterghast in Revengeance or Death Mode only
	CelestialOnion: Drops from Moon Lord
	InspirationEssence: Combine 1 Ocean Essence, 1 Death Essence, 1 Inferno Essence and 1 Inspiration Fragment at the Ancient Manipulator
